&lt;li&gt;Strong oncology clinical development experience preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience as the lead statistician for one or more clinical development projects, including pivotal studies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience supporting regulatory submissions (NDA/BLA/MAA) and interactions with health authorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;

